<h2>Install</h2>

<h3>Chrome extension</h3>
<p><a href="https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/dlhnalbfkikchkfedfneiimadommcnip">Chrome Web Store</a></p>

<h3>CLI</h3>
<pre><code>brew install hashiiiii/tap/prefablens</code></pre>
<pre><code>scoop bucket add hashiiiii https://github.com/hashiiiii/scoop-bucket
scoop install prefablens</code></pre>
<pre><code>mise use -g github:hashiiiii/PrefabLens</code></pre>

<h3>Unity Editor</h3>
<pre><code>openupm add com.hashiiiii.prefablens</code></pre>
<p>Or the Package Manager git URL: <code>https://github.com/hashiiiii/PrefabLens.git?path=editor</code></p>

<h3>Everything else</h3>
<p>Prebuilt binaries are on the <a href="https://github.com/hashiiiii/PrefabLens/releases">releases page</a>.</p>
